query:
INSERT INTO transportation (tripId, type, origin, destination, company, carModel, departureDate, arrivalDate, confirmationNumber, phone, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes, pickupLocation, returnLocation, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT tripId, 'car_rental', pickupLocation, returnLocation, company, carModel, pickupDate, returnDate, confirmationNumber, phone, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes, pickupLocation, returnLocation, NOW(), NOW()
FROM car_rentals
LIMIT 1;
